description:
The mystical allure of a pretty face has captivated men since the beginning of time. When that pretty face is packaged with a tight, hot young body sitting on your face there is no limit to the joy that will follow.

A steady stream of oversexed harlots display a unique perspective, peeling off layer after layer of sexual corruption. Hunting their nubile victims with the devilish decadence that only a true angel face can get away with, the sight of these sexy young things captivates the men and women who cross their paths in a heavy does of fantasy meets reality.
title: Pretty Tied Up
